{"tid":2159762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊明駕車撞穿80年歷史石牆  重建涉資25萬 專家指港府可索償","createTime":"2020-08-16T13:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T14:32:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0a170b218608df6a3eb22aeacd54cd8b8008f7cf","tid":2159762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:41:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/7B2WUSHS5JBIPM43AIOKTW6DUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2F7B2WUSHS5JBIPM43AIOKTW6DUM%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=376b7cf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2F7B2WUSHS5JBIPM43AIOKTW6DUM%2F&h=f4c74fa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/7B2WUSHS5JBIPM43AIOKTW6DUM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n楊明駕車撞穿80年歷史石牆 <br />\n重建涉資25萬 專家指港府可索償<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/b1cdzn4mkW1XAzE4vYLPtBagCzU=/1758x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J3IOKM6KA5E6FMT464U227IMXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fb1cdzn4mkW1XAzE4vYLPtBagCzU%3D%2F1758x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ3IOKM6KA5E6FMT464U227IMXM.jpg&h=cf86989e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■損毀石牆已圍封，路政署稱最快月底完成修復。夏家朗攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】TVB撐警藝人楊明8月8日凌晨炒車，其平治私家車在馬己仙峽道鏟上路邊，令一段三米石牆損毀。社區組織「城西關注組」成員張朝敦一直研究香港石牆，他翻查憲報分析，估計受損石牆在1930年代興建，至今逾80年歷史，「好彩有堅固石牆，先可以頂住楊生架車」。他認為，若當局有保留石塊，仍可修復舊貌。中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻計算，若要重造三米石牆，料涉及25萬元，港府可向楊明索償。<br />\n<br />\n張朝敦分析，損毀的石牆是戰前所建，有1920至30年代的特色，圍欄石塊較方正，頂部有圓拱修邊。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dRrf0dDNnJP9GDwYnpDfLnQWBUM=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KMYZMPNM6JDVNL554QEFD4VL5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdRrf0dDNnJP9GDwYnpDfLnQWBUM%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKMYZMPNM6JDVNL554QEFD4VL5E.jpg&h=d0316842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■撐警藝人楊明本月8日駕車自炒，事後由警員扶走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ODSXRVd3B-QDBs_lS_v-Q7RIXj0=/1372x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CJCJQAZEQZA5JHALANTH5S2KJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FODSXRVd3B-QDBs_lS_v-Q7RIXj0%3D%2F1372x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCJCJQAZEQZA5JHALANTH5S2KJM.jpg&h=1e3cb424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■馬己仙峽道的石牆建於戰前，石料由本地礦場出產。<br />\n<br />\n張指從傳媒相片可見，倒地石牆大致完整，修復不困難，如啟德明渠工程都。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻指，若要重換麻石修復，可在外地或中國輸入，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路政署：或會追討<br />\n<br />\n一般道路設施損毀後，由路政署地區維修分判商負責維修，成本包括臨時交通改道、圍封、物料等。張朝敦以路政署「天書。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路政署回覆稱，署方沒上述石牆建造年份資料，據古物古蹟辦事處資料，該石牆並非已獲評級的歷史建築。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路政署續稱，若有關設施因交通意外事故損毀，署方會在相。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"6d540d5e4c7e5b5245443a6cbccf11ee936e4add","tid":2159762,"uid":301050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"哇屌仆街<br />\n終生監禁啦屌"}]}